            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.804-4</ph> Repetitive acquisitions.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p class="- topic/p ">In order for repetitive acquisitions to be awarded through the 8(a) program, there must be separate offers and acceptances. This allows the SBA to determine-</p>
			      <ol id="d1203e16" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1217e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Whether the requirement should be a competitive 8(a) award;</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1217e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            A nominated 8(a) participant's eligibility, and whether or not it is the same 8(a) participant that performed the previous contract;</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1217e38" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The effect that contract award would have on the equitable distribution of 8(a) contracts; and</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1217e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Whether the requirement should continue under the 8(a) program.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
